{"tid":385218,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（環保撚）硬脂墮海，誰會拯救香港既沙灘","createTime":"2017-09-03T05:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T06:06:57.000Z","uid":24629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fee7b7abf074eb235f1dded00e12822e81bfda1","tid":385218,"uid":24629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:05:36.000Z","msg":"兩艘貨船上月3日在珠江口相撞，導致千噸棕櫚硬脂墮海，更不斷漂流來港，令香港多個沙灘、石灘受嚴重污染。事發至今一個月，《蘋果》重返南丫島，發現有不少硬脂污染物已融入沙灘。硬脂污染物或變成沙底「石頭」、或滲入石隙、或溶化並黏附於石面，料難以清除，屬瀕危綠海龜繁殖地的深灣成重災區。立法會議員斥當局清理行動太馬虎，環保人士憂南丫島生態受損，擔心海龜永不回來產卵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170903&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20141026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170903%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20141026&d=yTAR3Yr94ElvWOauvY8tmKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=241b3995\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170903%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20141026&h=a6c0fe92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20170903&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20141026</a><br />\n災後一個月　硬脂融入沙灘毀生態瀕危綠海龜恐難上岸產卵"},{"pid":"f637cf417b2753c8728d8a62856d8fdf77123fad","tid":385218,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"本身政府要做既野比班義工做咗但又做唔得晒，條數都唔知點claim對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4962b7dfac2d0904704186e9746492ed6d1221","tid":385218,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:31:49.000Z","msg":"機會來了！解放軍們！"},{"pid":"dd93c27a0a802fe13d6fed970005187af8014525","tid":385218,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"唔可以自然分解？"},{"pid":"5de29dd82cd5d9e97cea312f6108f5b55e5b9aad","tid":385218,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"大陸西唔撚洗負責？"},{"pid":"82888bde3bee3a2b3b959bd7